                            <comment id="13443176" author="mdrzal" created="Tue, 28 Aug 2012 14:03:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=jdcryans&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;jdcryans&quot;&gt;Jean-Daniel Cryans&lt;/a&gt; could you add a bit more detail on this?  We are looking for some work to pickup, and this might be of interest. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13443186" author="jdcryans" created="Tue, 28 Aug 2012 14:14:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m talking about this:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://docs.guava-libraries.googlecode.com/git/javadoc/com/google/common/cache/CacheBuilder.html#weigher(com.google.common.cache.Weigher&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://docs.guava-libraries.googlecode.com/git/javadoc/com/google/common/cache/CacheBuilder.html#weigher(com.google.common.cache.Weigher&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;You could write one that weights each block in terms of how big they are. Not all blocks are created equal.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14268471" author="clehene" created="Wed, 7 Jan 2015 23:08:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Marking as improvement. &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=jdcryans&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;jdcryans&quot;&gt;Jean-Daniel Cryans&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=ndimiduk&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;ndimiduk&quot;&gt;Nick Dimiduk&lt;/a&gt; is this still valid?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14269211" author="anoop.hbase" created="Thu, 8 Jan 2015 11:25:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;DoubleBlockCache  is no longer there in trunk. Closing this&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
